data.description: VA Assumable Mortgage. Gorgeous Home inside a residential Resort-Style community of Bellalago built by Taylor Morrison. This Java model with the 2nd floor option features 5 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms. The first thing you will notice as you drive up this stunning home is the stone pavers throughout the driveway and the Spanish Mediterranean roof tiles and the decorative stones façade. As you walk-in pass the elegant glass door, you will notice the beautiful color tiles with a breath-taking architectural wall designs with tray ceilings and elegant light fixtures.  As you continue walking straight ahead, you will notice the gorgeous built electric fireplace, along with sliding doors to your lanai for Family get togethers or to enjoy a cold pour margarita or a glass of wine while listening to all types of birds chirping.  The living room is right to the kitchen Open Floor plans.  Gorgeous kitchen with center island with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, with lots of cabinet space with pendant lights hanging by the center island with a lot of lighting.  If that is not all, Bellalago Community is within 30 minutes away from Walt Disney World and many major attraction parks.  Bellalago Community shares shores with Lake Toho of which is one of the 10 tops Lakes in the nation for Bass Fishing.  It has community boat ramp and slip, fishing pier, 24 hours gated community, walking and bike trails, fitness Centers and Aerobics room, fitness and Yoga instructors, tennis courts and basket ball courts, Volley-ball and barbecue area, dog parks, with two 7,000-foot clubhouses, Jr Olympic size pool and water parks including a ground Zero pool entry, You can enjoy nature while strolling a 1,300 foot boardwalk, our own bellalago Academy and Flip flops a full restaurant/bar to enjoy food or drinks by the pool side. Shopping stores right outside the gates. Too much to mention here.  Don't wait and call us today to schedule a showing at Bellalago where you will feel as if you are always on vacation.  Call us today.
